-Yes.

00:00:31.497 --> 00:00:34.067
<i> Queer Eye.</i> Now, the Fab Five,

00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:36.135
uh, you shoot a lot of this
in Georgia,

00:00:36.168 --> 00:00:38.071
-which is a red state.
-Mm-hmm. Mm-hmm.

00:00:38.104 --> 00:00:41.207
Is this goal of this show
transforming Trump's America

00:00:41.240 --> 00:00:43.276
