behind the curtain,

00:05:22.588 --> 00:05:23.823
and we're not gonna take it
anymore.

00:05:23.856 --> 00:05:25.891
He shows you the big hand,

00:05:25.924 --> 00:05:27.626
-he grabs you with the other.
-Yeah. Yeah.

00:05:27.659 --> 00:05:29.762
I hear that.
A new season of<i> Queer Eye</i>

00:05:29.795 --> 00:05:31.898
is now available on Netflix.
Karamo Brown.

